Title: mk_postgres: Fix 'Argument list too long'
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1720077731
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p35

The execution of large queries might run into an OS specific restriction
regarding the length of arguments. In order to bypass the above error we use
<code>psql -f &lt;FILE_PATH&gt;</code> instead of using <code>echo</code>, <code>cat</code> or similar for passing the
SQL to <code>pyql</code>.
